<p>Russian strikes across Ukraine hit a passenger train in the Kharkiv region and also damaged energy infrastructure overnight, according to Ukrainian officials. Prosecutors said remains of five people were found at the train strike site, and multiple outlets reported at least five fatalities from the train attack. Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy condemned the strike on the civilian train as “an act of terrorism,” as reporting noted the attack came only days after direct talks aimed at ending the war.</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/RKDAmVqSQt9MjTawTY_Qk2ez6EyHM-9ItQhZ_ngRmrKWK0V6a27QP1fAaBpZesmsYhCvvuZRkYXUfHqjXesY4Yup2SGyURJDpFbRwnfhrGrZ0ChKRXNpb0h-3L-gw4CkpnlCkAmR0gnX7at9VrHCJM2I-NQ5jWndNIQWe5l8eYE7-Ey4gmhaBHle-cQkfyaiSGL5-tU0W6AYMamzhUK7-o7R_NfwzGzvjgQbYJoaZfl16Dwz5g' alt='Aftermath imagery linked to reporting on Russian strikes in Ukraine, including the passenger-train attack.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Train capacity: Ukrainian officials said the hit carriage was on a train carrying nearly 200 passengers, underscoring the risk to civilians using public transport.</li><li>Wider toll: Separate reports on the same night described broader attacks elsewhere in Ukraine that brought the total deaths into the low double digits, indicating the train strike formed part of a wider wave of bombardment.</li><li>Energy targets: Ukrainian authorities said the overnight strikes also targeted energy infrastructure, continuing pressure on power supplies during winter.</li><li>Undermining talks: Zelenskyy argued the strike undercut efforts to end the war, as coverage linked the timing to recent direct negotiations between the sides.</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Ukrainian government: President Volodymyr Zelenskyy described the drone strike on a passenger train as “an act of terrorism” and framed it as harming efforts to end the war. (<a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/crkrpl4ngdzo'>BBC News</a>)</li><li>Ukrainian prosecutors: Prosecutors reported that fragments of five bodies were found at the train strike site in the Kharkiv region. (<a href='https://www.theguardian.com/world/2026/jan/27/russian-drone-strike-on-ukrainian-passenger-train-kills-five'>The Guardian</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.firstpost.com/world/russian-strike-on-ukrainian-passenger-train-kills-11-zelenskyy-calls-attack-an-act-of-terrorism-13973191.html'>&#x27;Act of terrorism&#x27;: Russian attacks across Ukraine kill 11, target passenger train</a> - firstpost.com</li><li><a href='http://www.euronews.com/2026/01/28/russia-strikes-passenger-train-in-ukraine-killing-five'>Russia strikes passenger train in Ukraine, killing five</a> - euronews.com</li><li><a href='https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/russian-strikes-in-ukraine-kill-12-target-passenger-train-10897564#publisher=newsstand'>Russian Strikes In Ukraine Kill 12, Target Passenger Train</a> - ndtv.com</li><li><a href='https://www.theguardian.com/world/2026/jan/27/russian-drone-strike-on-ukrainian-passenger-train-kills-five'>Russian drone strike on Ukrainian passenger train kills five</a> - theguardian.com</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/crkrpl4ngdzo'>Zelensky condemns Russian drone strike that killed five on passenger train</a> - bbc.com</li><li><a href='https://www.dw.com/en/zelenskyy-condemns-terrorism-after-russia-hits-train-in-ukraine/a-75686904'>Zelenskyy condemns &#x27;terrorism&#x27; after Russia hits train in Ukraine</a> - dw.com</li><li><a href='https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/russian-strikes-in-ukraine-kill-12-target-passenger-train/article70559186.ece'>Russian strikes in Ukraine kill 12, target passenger train</a> - thehindu.com</li></ul>